{"tid":1433541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[心心眼]彈弓、防毒面具對抗警察 反送中出現港版飢餓遊戲女神","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T00:33:30.000Z","uid":28942,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"971274a4d2ab1d85452d6113c95c41628cce0b43","tid":1433541,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/283/5d49405d39aad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F283%2F5d49405d39aad.jpg&h=56148994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個穿著黑色緊身衣、帶著防毒面具、拉緊彈弓對抗警察的女孩子，最近成了香港網路瘋傳的女主角。   圖 : 翻攝自桑普臉書<br />\n反送中運動出現了新女神，一個穿著黑色緊身衣、帶著防毒面具、拉緊彈弓對抗警察的女孩子，最近成了香港網路瘋傳的女主角。照片旁的貼文還寫著 : 香港女子，令人景仰，飢餓遊戲，光復香港。<br />\n<br />\n這名女子穿著緊身衣拉彈弓的姿態，的確與電影《飢餓遊戲》由珍妮佛勞倫斯飾演的女主角有幾分類似，兩人同樣穿著緊身衣，使用武器時的姿勢也同樣帥氣，只不過珍妮佛勞倫斯用的是致命的弓箭，而這名香港女子用的則是殺傷力較小的彈弓。<br />\n<br />\n在這次的反送中活動中，由蘇珊柯林絲所寫的反烏托邦青年小說，最後被改編成電影的《飢餓遊戲》，也成為象徵的精神之一，在香港民眾發起的連儂牆運動中，最常出現字句的就是《飢餓遊戲》中主角的對白：「If we burn, you burn with us.」(如果我們被焚，你也化為灰燼)。這句話被視為向中國警告：要侵犯香港的自由，香港人不會坐以待斃。<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆 (Lennon Walls) 的名字來自布拉格的一堵牆，1980年，前披頭士樂隊成員 約翰&middot;連儂 (John Lennon)被謀殺後，人們透過那堵牆向他致敬，最後成為捷克年青人表達渴望民主，對共產主義政權不滿的地方。<br />\n<br />\n此後民眾在城市各地的公共場所的牆壁上，用便利貼張貼數百甚至數千條標語，就被稱為連儂牆。從雨傘運動開始，香港也出現了連儂牆，而這次的反送中運動，更讓連儂牆在全港各地出現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-08-06/282393?f=ntk&amp;fbclid=IwAR2_l6sPE2dq5Na1JapLIu70Aenlu_Syv_1e_6EOgi4mASbkGDdBmxzpazM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2019-08-06%2F282393%3Ff%3Dntk%26fbclid%3DIwAR2_l6sPE2dq5Na1JapLIu70Aenlu_Syv_1e_6EOgi4mASbkGDdBmxzpazM&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9cemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=8663140d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-08-06/282393?f=ntk&amp;fbclid=IwAR2_l6sPE2dq5Na1JapLIu70Aenlu_Syv_1e_6EOgi4mASbkGDdBmxzpazM</a>"},{"pid":"f2fc255a3ee14944417537dec976bf1906574fb5","tid":1433541,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76960b29121ce9e4e1649ac071dd910bb4df8732","tid":1433541,"uid":28942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"真女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50c1065b3d92923925225718d108b2e8b8c2ead","tid":1433541,"uid":263038,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"我老婆嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b7d4034658d58219651d3508c9caa299bded5c","tid":1433541,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"548e2bb27d231b7f9dd651eb6dbdcf40b662ba8b","tid":1433541,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"179ae4b28068bd5c8777f205e67dff2b78583aaa","tid":1433541,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"24625494fb52f88c0b77322e73add17e4169d7c5","tid":1433541,"uid":114121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"Katniss <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1627da8b6fe09eb26594d4e0c05f2b1e6a2191e","tid":1433541,"uid":48947,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"睇左中出女神"},{"pid":"1c1c2c67dc8baf06ccd13a766657d1a5a3021dff","tid":1433541,"uid":139247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:51:31.000Z","msg":"好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07863e44c8dec01e08411de5f746379bae519bbf","tid":1433541,"uid":97949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"絲打好有型"},{"pid":"270cc9f7cc04de37d4eb349d78b558d87a860b2e","tid":1433541,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T00:33:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇下啦，2、3樓都仲有資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得睇下<br />\n<br />\n【正視聽：反思行動及行動數量】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680287\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680287</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFFDDQa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFFDDQa.png&h=9781c901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PZg9WR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PZg9WR.jpg&h=63c1787d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}